Usage: setInstancePlacementStatus [-help]
                                  -status {unplaced fixed placed cover softFixed}
                                  {-allHardMacros | -allPtnBlks | -allBlackBoxes | -name <instName(s)>}

-help                   # Prints out the command usage
-allBlackBoxes          # set all blackbox cells (bool, required)
-allHardMacros          # set all hard macros (bool, required)
-allPtnBlks             # set all partitions (bool, required)
-name <instName(s)>     # inistances names (string, required)
-status {unplaced fixed placed cover softFixed}
                        # placement status to be set (enum, required)